    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Paravoid</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival horror game set on a twisted space station where reality itself turns against you. Navigate warped, ever-changing corridors, face shapeshifting creatures disguised as friends, and manage your mental and physical health to survive the station's sinister secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295710/extras/bffdd333e7ee9b177007991a42332311.avif?t=1764601600\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295710/extras_big/bffdd333e7ee9b177007991a42332311.avif?t=1764601600 width=800 height=276 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shapeshifting Enemies:</strong> Mimic creatures disguise themselves as objects or people, keeping you in constant fear and doubt.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Non-Euclidean Exploration:</strong> Navigate environments that warp and shift, forcing you to adapt as the station itself changes around you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Impact of Death:</strong> Each death adds lasting mental strain, leading to hallucinations, distorted gameplay, and increased difficulty.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stress and Injury Management:</strong> Physical wounds limit your abilities, while high stress levels distort your perception of the world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Management:</strong> With limited inventory and scarce supplies, every decision could mean life or death.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295710/extras/eceb71a7c02e62004ddaaaa08ede4e36.poster.avif?t=1764601600\" width=800 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295710/extras/eceb71a7c02e62004ddaaaa08ede4e36.webm?t=1764601600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295710/extras/eceb71a7c02e62004ddaaaa08ede4e36.mp4?t=1764601600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
